}

^["stream"]{
 >>[2026-04-15 12:22] observe — The existing math hub is strong as a software-adjacent register but it does not yet branch into pure-math routes of its own.
 >>[2026-04-15 12:25] decide — Keep the pure-math cluster small and visual: topology for deformation, symmetry for invariants, combinatorics for finite arrangement.
 >>[2026-04-15 12:28] taste — The pages need compact field-guide energy rather than textbook density; each route should teach one visual habit of attention.
}

